  <brief_title>Ketamine Combination With Spinal Morphine for Post Thoracic Surgery Pain : A Randomized Control Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Low Dose Intraoperative Intravenous Ketamine Combination With Spinal Morphine for Post Thoracic Surgery Pain : A Randomized Control Study</official_title>
